    <title>Latex的学习（2）</title>
    <link href="https://neverlandsx.github.io/2021/01/12/Latex%20study2/"/>
    <id>https://neverlandsx.github.io/2021/01/12/Latex%20study2/</id>
    <published>2021-01-11T16:00:00.000Z</published>
    <updated>2021-01-12T15:25:42.542Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>此篇参考了刘海洋的《Latex入门》和中国ctex用户小组翻译的《一份不太简短的latex2 介绍》。</p><a id="more"></a><p>在Tex系统中已内置了部分的特殊字母输入方式，举个例子如：</p><figure class="highlight taggerscript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">caf<span class="symbol">\&#x27;</span>e <span class="symbol">\q</span>quad G<span class="symbol">\&quot;</span>odel <span class="symbol">\q</span>quad Anton<span class="symbol">\&#x27;</span>in Dvo<span class="symbol">\v</span>&#123;r&#125;<span class="symbol">\&#x27;</span>ak <span class="symbol">\q</span>quad <span class="symbol">\O</span> ster Vr<span class="symbol">\r</span>&#123;a&#125; <span class="symbol">\q</span>quad k<span class="symbol">\i</span> rka<span class="symbol">\u</span>&#123;g&#125;a<span class="symbol">\c</span>&#123;c&#125;                 <span class="variable">%注意有的特殊字母后面要加空格</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="variable"> </span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><img src="/2021/01/12/Latex%20study2/example1.jpg" class title="例子1"><p>系统内默认的特殊字符的输入方式：</p><p>若是还要其他未覆盖的字母需要输入时，就要使用babel宏包，调用命令为</p><figure class="highlight dust"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="xml">\usepackage[language]</span><span class="template-variable">&#123;babel&#125;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>上述命令中的language需换成相应的语言名字（english等），[]内也可以填’language2,language1’,language1为默认语言,非默认语言使用需采用格式使用：</p><figure class="highlight css"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">\<span class="selector-tag">textgreek</span>&#123; &#125;                 %这个命令不能用<span class="selector-tag">XeLatex</span>编译，会报错</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
    
